      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I can see why you'd want to avoid the ER, but taking oxy to dull the pain might not be the best idea. Oxy is a powerful painkiller, and taking it without a proper diagnosis could mask the real issue. If you're just experiencing bloating and discomfort, it's probably not a good idea to take something that could potentially interact with other meds or make the situation worse. Instead, try to get some rest and see if the pain subsides on its own. If it gets worse or you start to feel nauseous, then maybe it's time to come in.",
